author: Nexcell Pride
text:
Intense and greatest stream ever :_ã¡ã‚‡ã†ã¡ã‚‡:

Recently, Rushia-daitenshi is becoming more active at Minecraft's special activities... First with Tanabata at 2020 July 7th stream, later with Halloween activities in October, Sports festival in November (I missed the Sports festival streams, because I'm not used to seeing other Hololive's channels, with some exceptions with Korone-san, Shion-chan, Towa-chan, Luna-hime and the entire "Holofives" for few time... But lately I'm very focused at Rushia-daitenshi's streams, she has a special charming, and also I have my personal tastes outside Hololive, but preferably at independants. Sorry if I'm confessing this, but anyway Rushia is first at all)

At 0:18:38, the BGM changes... And also a flashback became...
The BGM remembered me about a private stream which was a Zatsudan, when Rushia cried meanwhile said "It's okay if you look at other girls, but please don't leave Rushia alone" 

Later at 0:26:53, BGM changed again. The selected BGM remembered me about the "Getting Over It" at June 2020 when Rushia suffered the corrupting save game, or the "Ark" stream at July 2020 when Rushia suffered the Guruguru at stream...

1:21:15 Rushia changes to Angry face. (Personally talking, I can confront this too) :_ãŠã“ãªã®ã§ã™:

1:21:48 Rushia changes to sad state... (I can't avoid that, it brokes my heart) :_ã‚ã›ã‚Š:

1:25:19 Returned to normal :_ãã‚…ã‚“:

But letting some details beside, the adventure is about the Xmas Tree... And crafting aditional materials for it. :_ã‚‹ã‚“ã‚‹ã‚“:

This deserves a "Part Deux", because it seems not finished yet...

And at "Supaachaato Orei Time", again a Naisupa battle, but the best part was the Rainbow Superchat.
Rushia-daitenshi also made many Transforms (Henshin) between the Second form (New Live2D) and the New Year Costume.
